  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegan butter in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and coriander seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add the sliced onions and cook until they are lightly browned.",
    "Add the katsuramuki-cut carrots and potatoes, and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the turmeric powder, salt, and ghee or vegan alternative, and stir well.",
    "Add the rinsed and drained arabic rice to the pan, and stir gently to combine with the vegetables and spices.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover the pan with a tight-fitting lid, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Turn off the heat, and let the biryani rest for 5 minutes before serving."
